  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 variant)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set to 3 following a re-scoping of the intended use to relative hemolysis comparison rather than absolute threshold demonstration. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been formally assessed; the Equivalency of input parameters factor is recorded as not-assessed on the grounds that the team considered patient-specific blood viscosity variability irrelevant to a pump-level CFD model — however this rationale has not been translated into a factorStatus of not-applicable as required by the standard, leaving a material epistemic gap at MRL 3.",
