      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented with uncertainty bounds; inlet flow rate and rotational speed match simulation boundary conditions within 2%.",
      "rationale": "All five operating points were tested with calibrated flow meters (±1.2%) and tachometers (±0.5%). Boundary condition matching is within tolerance. Test condition documentation satisfies MRL 3."
